196
00:16:31,180 --> 00:16:33,879
Itu demi kepentingan Putri Ari.

197
00:16:34,450 --> 00:16:36,420
Bagaimana Anda akan membalasku?

198
00:16:36,749 --> 00:16:37,889
Membalasmu?

199
00:16:39,450 --> 00:16:42,889
Kamu meniru Yu Ra sekarang?

200
00:16:44,029 --> 00:16:46,600
Kamu pikir siapa dirimu?

201
00:16:46,899 --> 00:16:49,159
Lakukan saja sesuai perintah. Dasar lancang.

202
00:16:50,269 --> 00:16:51,330
Tujuh tahun lalu,

203
00:16:52,830 --> 00:16:54,139
ada pesta penyempurnaan istana baru

204
00:16:54,139 --> 00:16:56,269
di hari kematian Permaisuri So Hyun.

205
00:16:56,840 --> 00:17:00,109
Semua pergi ke istana baru untuk menyiapkan pesta,

206
00:17:00,940 --> 00:17:04,250
