207
00:17:04,609 --> 00:17:06,050
Apa maksudmu?

208
00:17:06,919 --> 00:17:09,219
Saat tidak menemukan dia yang hamil tua, aku cemas,

209
00:17:09,250 --> 00:17:10,550
